query:
SELECT ws.id, ws.clientId, ws.stepId, ws.stepTitle, ws.completed, c.name 
FROM workflowSteps ws 
JOIN clients c ON ws.clientId = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%jose%' OR c.name LIKE '%josé%'
ORDER BY ws.id 
LIMIT 10;
